<%- include("head", {title: "Add a new product"}) %>
<h1>Add a product</h1>
Fill in a name for the product, and the slug for the URL. The other fields can be filled in when the release is created.
<form method="post" action="/sa/createProduct">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="form-group col">
            <label for="name">Name</label>
            <input required type="text" class="form-control" id="name" name="name" placeholder="Name" onblur="updateSlugMaybe(this)">
        </div>
        <div class="form-group col">
            <label for="slug">Slug</label>
            <input required type="text" class="form-control" id="slug" name="slug" placeholder="Slug" onblur="slugBlur(this)" pattern="^[0-9A-Za-z-]+$" value="<%= slug %>">
            <small class="form-text text-muted">
                Alphanumeric characters and hyphen only. This must be unique.
            </small>
        </div>
    </div>
    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Submit</button>
</form>
